      *------------------
       1000-PROCESS-DATE.
      *------------------
 
           IF  L1680-COMPUTE-DAYS-BETWEEN
               PERFORM  2000-DAYS-BETWEEN
                   THRU 2000-DAYS-BETWEEN-X
